description._content: Original Collection: Corvallis, Oregon Photographic Collection (P 51) Item Number: P51:40 Image Description: The Majestic theater is now located in the Porter Building. The store at the right was Witham's Ladies Shop. Johnson Porter's 1915 Hudson is shown in right front. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
